Processor				-		a class that implements that interface org.apache.camel.Processor from camel-api\
							only a single method, process() that works on an exchange\
Data Format				-		a class that implements org.apache.camel.spi.DataFormat\
							2 methods - marshal and unmarshal\
Endpoint				-		is a URI of some sort like \'93direct:start\'94, \'93seda:Gaz\'94 that is provided by a component\
Producer				-		a class that implements the Producer interface and can send data from a route to an external system		[the external system could be another route]\
							it appears at the end of a route\
Consumer				-		a class that implements the Consumer interface and can receive data from an external system 			[the external system could be another route]\
							it appears at the beginning of a route\
