ENTERPRISE INTEGRATION PATTERNS\
\
Content Based Router		-		.choice().when()					[uses a predicate to determine how to process a message]\
Multicast				-		.multicast()\
Wiretap				-		.wireTap()\
RecipientList				-		.recipientList(), .bean(RecipientListBean)	[uses an expression to determine how to process a message]\
Message Filter			-		.filter()							[uses a predicate to determine how to process a message]\
Content Enricher			-		.pollEnrich(), .enrich()\
Message Translator			-		.process(), .bean(), .transform()\
Service Activator			-									[the Camel Bean component is the Camel implementation of the Service Activator Pattern]\
DynamicTo				-		.toD()							[uses an expression to determine how to process a message, used for single destinations]\
Routing Slip				-		.routingSlip()						[For routing messages dynamically based on some logic, this EIP computes the slip up front]\
Dynamic Router			-		.dynamicRouter					[For routing messages dynamically based on some logic]\
Load Balancer			-		.loadBalance()\
Idempotent Consumer		-									[uses an expression to determine how to process a message]\
Aggregator				-		.aggregate()\
Splitter				-		.split()\
Composed Message Processor	-									[combination of aggregator and splitter]\
\
\
\
\
AGGREGATOR EIP\
\
Correlation Identifier		-	an \'91expression\'92 which determines which messages belong together\
Completion Condition		-	a \'91predicate\'92 OR time based condition that determines when the result message should be sent		[size, timeout, interval, predicate, force, strategy, consumer]\
Aggregation Strategy		-	a strategy that specifies how to combine the messages into a single message\
\
aggregate is a place where incoming messages are stored\
\
Camel enriches the published Exchange with the completion details\
\
